collection.name: CyberKongz VX
collection.description:
**NOTE: around 7K CyberKongz VX are bridged to our [collection](https://opensea.io/collection/cyberkongz-vx-polygon) on Polygon and thus held by the bridge contract!**
[CyberKongz](https://opensea.io/collection/cyberkongz) VX are unique and randomly generated 3D NFT Social Avatars for the Metaverse and upcoming interoperability with The Sandbox.
Some appear normal. Some look weird. Some are just damn cool! Maybe some even look familiar!

[More CyberKongz Collections!](https://opensea.io/collection/cyberkongz-nfts)  
[Website](https://cyberkongz.com) | [Twitter](https://twitter.com/cyberkongz) | [Discord](https://discord.gg/cyberkongz)
